42
00:03:52,107 --> 00:03:53,692
Kita harus beli kado ulang tahun Sol-i.

43
00:03:54,526 --> 00:03:56,528
Kawan berulang tahun? Kapan?

44
00:03:56,611 --> 00:03:57,821
Sabtu pekan depan.

45
00:03:58,780 --> 00:04:00,782
