119
00:07:54,391 --> 00:07:56,059
Hei, Kawan!

120
00:07:56,142 --> 00:07:58,395
Apa? Woo Dae-sung!

121
00:07:59,980 --> 00:08:02,440
Apa yang kau lakukan
sampai tak sempat makan malam?

122
00:08:02,524 --> 00:08:03,900
Padahal makan di rumah saja.

123
00:08:04,651 --> 00:08:06,945
Aku gagal mendapat kerja paruh waktu

124
00:08:07,028 --> 00:08:09,072
dan kemari karena lapar sekali.

125
00:08:09,155 --> 00:08:10,991
Kau bekerja paruh waktu di sini?

126
00:08:11,992 --> 00:08:13,284
Aku sungguh iri.

127
00:08:13,368 --> 00:08:15,161
- Kenapa kau cari kerja?
- Itu.

128
00:08:15,245 --> 00:08:16,955
Aku ingin beli sesuatu.

129
00:08:18,540 --> 00:08:22,002
Aku baru ingat.
Dae-sung, kuingin menanyakan sesuatu.

130
00:08:22,085 --> 00:08:23,378
Apa?

131
00:08:24,087 --> 00:08:27,424
Kau tulis apa saat kita
main buka rahasia waktu itu?

132
00:08:32,178 --> 00:08:33,263
Aku…

133
00:08:34,431 --> 00:08:35,640
Apa, ya?

134
00:08:37,684 --> 00:08:41,271
Aku menulis, "Aku sangat suka hamburger."
Kurasa begitu.

135
00:08:41,354 --> 00:08:43,773
Sungguh? Kau jujur, 'kan? Tidak bohong?

136
00:08:43,857 --> 00:08:45,942
Tentu saja aku jujur.

137
00:08:47,485 --> 00:08:48,486
Baiklah.

138
00:08:51,031 --> 00:08:52,032
Terima kasih.

139
00:08:57,162 --> 00:08:58,163
Heon!

140
00:09:01,583 --> 00:09:04,627
Tadinya aku hendak memberi ini
saat kencan Sabtu ini.

141
00:09:10,091 --> 00:09:12,469
Kejutan! Ini seragam
bertanda tangan Park Ji-sung.

142
00:09:13,053 --> 00:09:15,138
Aku beli ini karena tak dapat tiket MUFC,

143
00:09:15,221 --> 00:09:17,098
