144
00:09:17,682 --> 00:09:19,100
Tidak perlu. Untukmu saja.

145
00:09:20,351 --> 00:09:22,812
Kenapa? Kau suka Park Ji-sung, 'kan?

146
00:09:22,896 --> 00:09:24,189
Aku tidak butuh.

147
00:09:28,610 --> 00:09:30,945
Aku sudah bersusah payah membelinya.

148
00:09:31,446 --> 00:09:33,990
- Aku minta tolong Dae-sung untuk beli…
- Berapa?

149
00:09:36,534 --> 00:09:37,410
Seharga 50.000 won.

150
00:09:45,001 --> 00:09:47,128
Puas? Jadi, berhenti ikuti aku.

151
00:09:48,046 --> 00:09:49,756
Hari Sabtu pun aku takkan datang.

152
00:09:50,465 --> 00:09:51,382
Jangan tunggu aku.

153
00:10:26,584 --> 00:10:27,919
Jin-hwan, ada apa?

154
00:10:33,758 --> 00:10:34,968
Kenapa menghindariku?

155
00:10:35,552 --> 00:10:37,971
- Aku tak menghindar.
- Sekarang pun menghindar.

156
00:10:38,054 --> 00:10:39,013
Lihat mataku.

157
00:10:39,097 --> 00:10:40,390
Tidak.

158
00:10:40,473 --> 00:10:43,977
Aku hanya tak bisa melihatmu
karena kau terlalu bersinar.

159
00:10:44,853 --> 00:10:46,938
Berhenti bercanda dan jujurlah. Ada apa?

160
00:10:47,897 --> 00:10:49,232
Soal itu…

161
00:10:50,525 --> 00:10:51,568
