162
00:10:52,610 --> 00:10:54,487
Uang itu hilang.

163
00:10:56,156 --> 00:10:58,783
Astaga, dasar bodoh! Kenapa bisa hilang?

164
00:10:58,867 --> 00:11:02,120
Maaf, Ha-young.
Lebih tepatnya bukan hilang,

165
00:11:02,203 --> 00:11:03,621
- tapi dicuri.
- Benar!

166
00:11:04,539 --> 00:11:05,790
Kita harus ganti strategi.

167
00:11:17,844 --> 00:11:19,012
Ada apa?

168
00:11:19,095 --> 00:11:20,054
Cha Heon,

169
00:11:20,138 --> 00:11:23,224
