berusaha mencari tiket MUFC, 'kan?

170
00:11:24,058 --> 00:11:26,311
Menurutmu, demi siapa
dia bersusah payah begitu?

171
00:11:27,437 --> 00:11:30,231
Di hari pertandingan MU
ada Dream Concert juga.

172
00:11:30,315 --> 00:11:32,567
Kulihat semua penyanyi
kesukaan Sol-i tampil.

173
00:11:34,444 --> 00:11:35,361
Hei,

174
00:11:35,445 --> 00:11:37,196
kau tahu Sabtu ini
ulang tahun Sol-i, 'kan?

175
00:11:44,287 --> 00:11:45,747
SMA YUIL

176
00:11:51,878 --> 00:11:54,130
MARI BUAT SEKOLAH MENYENANGKAN
BAGI SEMUA ORANG!

177
00:11:54,213 --> 00:11:55,340
Selamat malam.

178
00:11:55,423 --> 00:11:56,925
Kau tahu di mana Dae-sung?

179
00:11:58,426 --> 00:12:00,887
Soal itu…

180
00:12:01,596 --> 00:12:03,431
Tak lama lagi ada pertandingan,

181
00:12:03,514 --> 00:12:06,351
tapi sudah beberapa hari
dia mangkir berlatih

182
00:12:07,101 --> 00:12:08,645
dan tak pulang ke rumah.

183
00:12:09,187 --> 00:12:11,397
Pak Pelatih.

184
00:12:11,481 --> 00:12:13,691
Tolong jangan marahi Dae-sung.

185
00:12:13,775 --> 00:12:16,361
Dia anak baik yang hanya kenal renang.

186
00:12:16,444 --> 00:12:20,323
Ketika main bersama kami pun,
dia tak pernah mangkir berlatih.

187
00:12:20,406 --> 00:12:22,909
Selain itu, walau dia senang
bermain dengan kami,

188
00:12:22,992 --> 00:12:25,078
tapi dia paling bahagia saat berenang.

189
00:12:27,622 --> 00:12:30,917
