194
00:12:54,941 --> 00:12:56,401
Satu paket hamburger <i>bulgogi</i>.

195
00:13:01,406 --> 00:13:02,240
Kartu diterima.

196
00:13:44,449 --> 00:13:45,575
Hari ini…

197
00:13:46,325 --> 00:13:47,827
