Dia…

201
00:14:25,907 --> 00:14:26,908
Ayahku.

202
00:14:49,555 --> 00:14:50,765
Jeong Jin-hwan.

203
00:14:52,225 --> 00:14:53,226
Soal…

204
00:14:54,977 --> 00:14:56,729
tiket Dream Concert.

205
00:14:58,064 --> 00:14:59,315
Kau tahu dijual di mana?

206
00:14:59,816 --> 00:15:02,568
CHA HEON

207
00:15:10,952 --> 00:15:12,286
<i>Halo?</i>

208
00:15:13,246 --> 00:15:14,664
Apa menu makan siang besok?

209
00:15:14,747 --> 00:15:17,375
- Apa?
<i>- Apa menu kantin besok?</i>

210
00:15:19,043 --> 00:15:20,920
Nasi kari ayam.

211
00:15:21,629 --> 00:15:22,505
Kenapa tanya?

212
00:15:23,172 --> 00:15:25,425
Aku hanya ingin tahu.

213
00:15:26,092 --> 00:15:28,761
Begitu rupanya.

214
00:15:28,845 --> 00:15:30,054
<i>Selamat tidur.</i>

215
00:15:30,638 --> 00:15:31,597
Sampai besok.

216
00:15:48,239 --> 00:15:50,741
