217
00:15:55,455 --> 00:15:56,831
Putriku.

218
00:15:56,914 --> 00:15:58,291
Kau tahu ayah beli apa?

219
00:15:59,792 --> 00:16:02,378
Ini dia! Ayah beli dua.

220
00:16:02,462 --> 00:16:04,505
Hebat! Sungguh?

221
00:16:04,589 --> 00:16:07,091
Kenapa ekspresimu begitu? Ada masalah?

222
00:16:07,175 --> 00:16:09,010
Tidak apa.

223
00:16:09,093 --> 00:16:11,512
Terima kasih, Ayah.

224
00:16:17,935 --> 00:16:18,936
Shin Sol-i.

225
00:16:19,604 --> 00:16:20,563
Ya?

226
00:16:23,316 --> 00:16:24,317
Pagi!

227
00:16:25,276 --> 00:16:27,778
Ya, pagi!

228
00:16:41,292 --> 00:16:42,710
Pagi, Kawan!

229
00:16:42,793 --> 00:16:43,961
Hai, pagi!

230
00:16:45,213 --> 00:16:46,839
Kemarin kau pulang, 'kan?

231
00:16:46,923 --> 00:16:49,800
Ya. Semua berkatmu. Terima kasih.

232
00:16:49,884 --> 00:16:51,344
Aku teman terbaik, 'kan?

233
00:16:51,427 --> 00:16:53,971
